XDOTOOL HOTCORNERS
VIDEO: http://youtu.be/r4iSPrCpBRE

xfce gnome like behaviour
xdotool
- hotcorners

skippy-xdf (from the AUR)
- expo

xfdashboard

example scripts:

#!/bin/bash
xdotool behave_screen_edge top-left exec /usr/bin/xfdashboard &
## gnome-shell like
------------------------------
#!/bin/bash
xdotool behave_screen_edge top-right exec /usr/bin/skippy-xd --toggle-window-picker
## expose effect
------------------------------
#!/bin/bash
xdotool behave_screen_edge bottom-left exec xfce4-popup-whiskermenu &
## whisker menu

